        <Parent_String>whiteprints [300028517], reprographic copies [300028477], information artifacts by physical form [300137960], information artifacts [300230425], information forms (objects) [300220751], Information Forms (hierarchy name) [300026029], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
